                     <additions ana="low">
                        <p>Leaf 67r is a Titlepage in the hand of <name type="person" key="BogBen001">Bogi Benediktsson</name> and on leaf <locus from="68r" facs="#Lbs04-0360-0068r" to="68r">68r</locus> there is
